QuestData.Title: Explorers' League Document (2 of 6)
QuestData.Description: The document bears the Explorers' League crest and seems to detail potential dig sites in Loch Modan. Sooty smudges lead you to believe it was likely stolen by the Dark Iron spies in the area.$B$BYou recall mention of missing documents at the Explorers' League building in Thelsamar.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return the Explorers' League Document to Torren Squarejaw in Thelsamar.
QuestData.RewardText: Well look at that. You found one of our stolen documents!$B$BWe're much obliged for its return. Hopefully a bit of gold will suit your fancy for the finder's fee?
